All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary Enum Summary 
    Class Description
    AllNewsQuery
    Class contains query forming functions for everything news endpoint
    ApiQuery
    Interface contains the methods for creating, editing, and making API calls to newsAPI
    Article
    Implemented by single news/source class also contains functionality to show menu
    Authentication
    This class contains static methods and session variables related to authenticating user If currUser is equal to guestUser, then user is not authenticated.
    DateUtilities
    Class contains the static methods to format/parse dates
    FileHandling
    Contains static methods used to handle reading and writing objects to and from files
    Globals
    Contains the globally accessible variables for the project
    MainApplication
    This class contains the main menu and redirects to various functionalities of the project.
    News
    Class displays details of a single news object from a JsonObject
    NewsEndpoint
    This contains two constants for news filters EVERYTHING: used to make news queries with more than one filter TOP-HIGHLIGHTS: used to make simple filter with language, country etc.
    NewsFeedApplication
    Main class which invokes the application
    NewsQuery
    Contains all the utility functions for making news based API calls
    OfflineArticles<T extends Article>
    Stores the list of news or source for offline, bookmark and subscriptions
    ShowsMenu
    Implemented by any class which displays main menu
    Source  
    SourceQuery
    Class contains query forming methods to request and return source objects
    TopNewsQuery
    Class contains query forming functions for top-headline news endpoint
    User
    User class contains the details of an user This class is serialized in the Users details file.
